snippet.title: Best VGM 791 - Batman: Return of the Joker - Ending
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 285 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nFsoCfGij0Y&feature=related

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

NES
Batman: Return of the Joker (1991)
Ending
Naoki Kodaka, Nobuyuki Hara & Shinichi Seya
